'''唐·奥伯道夫'''（{{lang-en|'''Donald Oberdorfer Jr.'''}}，{{bd|1931年|5月28日|2015年|7月23日|catIdx=D}}），是[[美国|美国]]《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》资深记者。

==生平==
1931年出生于[[美国|美国]][[亚特兰大|亚特兰大]]，毕业于[[普林斯顿大学|普林斯顿大学]]，[[约翰斯·霍普金斯大学|约翰斯·霍普金斯大学]]国际学院教授。<ref>[https://www.piie.com/blogs/north-korea-witness-transformation/don-oberdorfer-1931-2015 Don Oberdorfer 1931-2015 | PIIE]</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/national/don-oberdorfer-longtime-diplomatic-correspondent-for-the-post-dies-at-84/2015/07/24/a9b2f404-314c-11e5-97ae-30a30cca95d7_story.html |title=Don Oberdorfer, longtime diplomatic correspondent for The Post, dies at 84 |access-date=2021-03-25 |archive-date=2021-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208140702/https://www.washingtonpost.com/national/don-oberdorfer-longtime-diplomatic-correspondent-for-the-post-dies-at-84/2015/07/24/a9b2f404-314c-11e5-97ae-30a30cca95d7_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.38north.org/2015/07/rcarlin073015/ |title=Don Oberdorfer: History’s Gracious Scribe |access-date=2021-03-25 |archive-date=2020-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200116034119/https://www.38north.org/2015/07/rcarlin073015/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://vva.org/arts-of-war/book-news/don-oberdorfer-1931-2015/ |title=Don Oberdorfer, 1931-2015 {{!}} Vietnam Veterans of America |access-date=2021-03-25 |archive-date=2020-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926045805/https://vva.org/arts-of-war/book-news/don-oberdorfer-1931-2015/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

